入款(<%= deposits.length %>笔) :
<% deposits.forEach((item, index) => { %><code><%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %></code>  <strong><%= item.amount %></strong>
<% }) %>
下发（<%= withdraws.length %>笔）:
<% withdraws.forEach((item, index) => { %><code><%= new Date(item.createdAt).toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN', { hour12: false }) %></code>  <strong><%= item.amount %></strong>
<% }) %>
总入款: <%= deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %> <%= unit %>
费率：<%= (feeRate).toFixed(2) %>%
USD汇率: <%= exchangeRate %>
应下发: <%= (deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) * exchangeRate * (1 - feeRate)).toFixed(2) %> <%= unit %>
总下发: <%= withdraws.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) %> <%= unit %>
余: <%= (deposits.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0) - withdraws.reduce((sum, item) => sum + item.amount, 0)).toFixed(2) %> <%= unit %>